extends ./base.pug

block content
  p(style="margin:0 0 10px;color:#6b7280;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;") Secure reset
  h1(style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:28px;color:#111827;")= subject
  p(style="margin:0 0 14px;line-height:1.7;") Hi #{firstName},
  p(style="margin:0 0 24px;line-height:1.7;color:#4b5563;")= intro
  a(
    href=url
    style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;background-color:#2f6b3f;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;font-weight:700;"
  )= buttonLabel
  p(style="margin:24px 0 8px;line-height:1.7;color:#6b7280;")
    | This link is time-sensitive. If the button does not work, copy and paste this URL:
  p(style="margin:0 0 18px;word-break:break-all;")
    a(href=url style="color:#2f6b3f;text-decoration:none;")= url
  div(style="padding:14px 16px;background-color:#e8f5e9;border-radius:12px;color:#2e7d32;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;")
    | If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
